# Quarto notebooks contain LaTeX math blocks that mdformat corrupts
# (doubles backslashes, strips \, thin-space, escapes subscript underscores)
*.qmd

# Model derivation/review docs and openspec specs also embed LaTeX math
# and hit the same corruption (e.g. z_{rep} -> z\_{rep}); same fix as above.
experiment/**/updates/**/*.md
openspec/specs/**/*.md
